			<p>Every year, around 400 underprivileged children from Leeds are given a much needed holiday from difficult home lives and tough family circumstances. They get the opportunity to enjoy playing, make new friends and focus on being children, away from the pressures they face day-to-day. The LCC has been providing and caring for these children since 1904.</p>

			<p>I was commissioned by Fat Beehive to design a new website for the LCC that reflects this important work: a site that gives families, schools and financial supporters a central, online point of reference, giving them all the information they need about the LCC.</p>

